Restaurant and Special Events Manager (Banquets and Catering)<br>
<br>
We are The Grill on The Alley, a nationwide upscale restaurant chain that serves straightforward, classic American cuisine. Our reputation of offering first-rate fare, attentive service, and a familiar, dignified atmosphere is without equal in the industry. We currently have locations in Beverly Hills, Westlake Village, San Jose, Chicago, Dallas and Aventura, FL. To learn more about us go to <a href="http://thegrill.com" rel="nofollow">http://thegrill.com</a>.<br>
<br>
We have an opening at The Grill on The Alley in Chicago for a Restaurant and Special Events Manager.  The following experience is desirable:<br>
<br>
 * Outside sales of restaurants Private Dining and Catering capabilities<br>
 * Supervising events and event staff<br>
 * Proactively executing flawless customer satisfaction<br>
 * Leads a scheduled shift in the restaurant<br>
 * Coordinate Private Dining and Catering events<br>
 * Administrates restaurant office functions for special events including but not limited to:<br>
 * Responding to event orders<br>
 * Cold calling for events<br>
 * Creating banquet event orders and banquet packets<br>
 * Follow up on past events<br>
 * Walk though with clients<br>
<br>
Required Skills:<br>
<br>
* Great sales skills * Good private dining and catering marketing skills * Proactive guest issue prevention/guest relations skills * Knowledge of restaurant POS system and Banquet system management operations * Experience in managing a restaurant shift * Proficient in Word and Excel * Must have a good understanding of restaurant office functions * An open availability (days, nights, weekends) * Must be committed to our mission and culture * Familiar with Catering programs a plus.<br>
<br>
Please apply online ONLY at: <a href="https://dailygrill-ats.silkroad.com/epostings/index.cfm?fuseaction=app.jobInfo&amp;version=1&amp;jobid=306233" rel="nofollow">https://dailygrill-ats.silkroad.com/epostings/index.cfm?fuseaction=app.jobInfo&amp;version=1&amp;jobid=306233</a><br>
<br>
For more career information go to: <a href="https://thegrillcareers.silkroad.com" rel="nofollow">https://thegrillcareers.silkroad.com</a><br>
<br>
The Grill on The Alley offers a great family work environment, competitive compensation, exceptional learning opportunities and exciting incentives and benefits. Be part of the best dining experience in Chicago.<br>
<br>
EOE    </section>

